{"tid":1517920,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【荃灣JJ入嚟】全．城匯業主TG Group Admin 打壓鳩叫自由","createTime":"2019-08-30T05:25:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T11:35:53.000Z","uid":127739,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cb8f42351c9b7daec33c18df4abbb1c880931eb7","tid":1517920,"uid":127739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"代朋友Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n最近手足們都響應晚上10點鳩叫活動<br />\n咁都預左會有藍絲唔鍾意架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁一班手足嗌左幾日<br />\n屋苑個業主Group就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[叉開少少話題]<br />\n屋苑個業主Group有藍有黃<br />\nGroup Admin大約十個八個咁上下<br />\n有一個admin就成日發表d偉論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nd擦鞋狗會叫佢做「主席」<br />\n個group過去有業主<br />\n提起政治話題搞到嘈交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自此大家唔想嘈交之下<br />\n就傾好左大家唔講政治話題<br />\n但可以share屋苑資訊 (eg. 荃葵青遊行tear gas殺到屋苑附近)<br />\n<br />\n[好啦返返嚟]<br />\n8月28日<br />\n屋苑個業主Group Admin 無啦啦send左msg出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">各位親愛的鄰居，大家好，經過上星期日大家親眼目睹家園附近烽煙四起既情況，相信大家都有唔同感受，唯幸全城沒有被波及，安然渡過，亦感謝大家都能在這個群組內表現克制，我相信大家都會認同一點，無論大家持任何政見都會懷著愛香港、愛全城既心。<br />\n<br />\n我留意到近日各區發起不同形式既叫口號活動，相信我們有鄰居參與其中亦不難理解，唯這些口號可能會令一些鄰居引起反感、不滿，甚至引發罵戰，亦可能會影響鄰居休息。<br />\n<br />\n所以我希望在此作出呼籲，不要把全城拉入政治漩渦裡面，政治問題政治解決，秉承我們致力保持屋苑內和諧既初心，繼續安居全城。</span>//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1BnwOz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1BnwOz.jpg&h=ecf4cb7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌 睇到既第一個反應<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">喂 好撚嘔心啊</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//無論大家持任何政見都會懷著愛香港、愛全城既心。//<br />\n<br />\n你老味唔好講野下下全城全城啦<br />\n你估大家好撚熟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前唔講政見 冇所謂 都廢事見到個gp嘈<br />\n乜原來而家居民連鳩叫權利都冇?<br />\n即係咁 又未到11點 <br />\n我叫床太大聲叫左「光復香港時代革命」又得唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你老味你憑咩代表全．城匯業主?</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//這些口號可能會令一些鄰居引起反感、不滿，<br />\n甚至引發罵戰，亦可能會影響鄰居休息。//<br />\n<br />\n你條撚樣仲要扮中立 黃藍意見都聽<br />\n<br />\n//不要把全城拉入政治漩渦裡面//<br />\n<br />\n最後就要黃既業主收聲?<br />\n生活所有野都同政治有關架收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者 佢呼籲完 的確令屋苑少左人嗌<br />\n得返零星少數人嗌<br />\n今日「主席」又sd msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//<span style=\"color: red;\">另外，經早兩日公開呼籲過鄰居保持和諧，唔好嗌口號，鄰居們普遍都承諾過唔參加，唯我地留意到有小數鄰居參與，估計是未加入群組既鄰居或租客，我懇請大家保持冷靜，同時小心有類似其他屋苑的高空擲物既情況，多加留意並保護好自身安全，admin們會進行觀察並適時跟進。<br />\n#尊重別人自由<br />\n#尊重別人不想聽既權利<br />\n#和諧全城</span>//<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZnFfRVk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZnFfRVk.jpg&h=0280ef3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嘩屌你 講野愈黎愈難聽<br />\n你當你邊位啊? admin們會進行觀察並適時跟進?<br />\n選撚左你做法團主席呀而家?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟乜野進? 洗唔洗報警拉哂鳩叫既人?<br />\n你叫人 #尊重別人自由<br />\n喂大佬 你有唔想聽既權利<br />\n但我都有叫既權利喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：冇鳩叫 因為聲帶唔好嗌唔到<br />\n但非常支持手足鳩叫every night<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日我講出黎係因為我地忍撚夠喇<br />\n政府日日散播白色恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解我住既地方要自我審查<br />\n我都未撚聽過有法團叫人唔好鳩叫<br />\n但你都唔撚係法團就出哂聲叫我地收聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我要為手足捍衛我地鳩叫既權利</span><br />\n大家唔好驚佢就妥協 我地要以鳩叫話俾佢知<br />\n我地唔撚妥你啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全．城匯 業主/居民 我地要捍衛我地既權利啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd1d4b1d8654af1ba4b493b4de17c502b4ae29c2","tid":1517920,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mhik2fq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMhik2fq.gif&h=7b54c7c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=6e9068a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=07903d05\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=Fe1Xron1KfJbBj576sEg8j4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=f090d0c0\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"b31c253dd3ec94839bb9b3395cb134c6968d03ce","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n哇 佢當自己係咩？主席？<br />\n<br />\n有法團喇咩？<br />\n<br />\n推佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"039f900bdd833fbc8bafcd3eaeb4574a1dbb94c0","tid":1517920,"uid":88728,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:40:10.000Z","msg":"賣鳩佢過黎海之戀啦<br />\n海之戀admin 好撚好, 又靚"},{"pid":"47f8a3a640c5c0764176efb23bda5b0bc4595a87","tid":1517920,"uid":27961,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T05:48:38.000Z","msg":"<strong>代朋友回應<br />\n<br />\n主席唔係藍人</strong><br />\