" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb54f60a30c4836fc94a50b55462a16ae6d98cc6","tid":1517920,"uid":127739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T07:43:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cc0f4c6c69cc058eaa07baf8116113522f11f3","tid":1517920,"uid":219445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T08:27:02.000Z","msg":"最緊要係唔好影響樓價!"},{"pid":"4c799b7e7c969430591796a13165aeddf8ae5fa1","tid":1517920,"uid":70494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"全城匯好似全部窗都係隔音<br />\n咁撚阻你休息可以關窗"},{"pid":"a775e121aa6b6f7d03a1ecdf44e027968c4e0f02","tid":1517920,"uid":70494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:11:04.000Z","msg":"利申租客，唔係業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e408510ee2b5300ba26a64fd7b351ee55746cb1","tid":1517920,"uid":112416,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:23:27.000Z","msg":"欣賞樓主堅持打嗰一點"},{"pid":"2eaa62dc3be75adf6d143bf3095aa39bbad1321f","tid":1517920,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"嗌下都唔滿意咁搞鬼"},{"pid":"28f83fa193c35724056705e001ed7dfa7448e5fc","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4c799b7e7c969430591796a13165aeddf8ae5fa1","tid":1517920,"uid":70494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:10:48.000Z","msg":"全城匯好似全部窗都係隔音<br />\n咁撚阻你休息可以關窗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:49:35.000Z","msg":"岩啊<br />\n全部都係雙層玻璃黎<br />\n其實依家咁熱，夜晚一定開緊冷氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔特登行出露台根本唔會聽到<br />\n唔岩聽咪閂窗囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：業主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edcc1036df1b96574f313ab249498caf8291ae2a","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2eaa62dc3be75adf6d143bf3095aa39bbad1321f","tid":1517920,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T10:27:44.000Z","msg":"嗌下都唔滿意咁搞鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T13:51:07.000Z","msg":"最嬲係啊主席： &ldquo;#尊重別人的自由&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n但佢根本無尊重過其他人既自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2737f2e63166d664c4f1b119af76faf7a6d4823","tid":1517920,"uid":127739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"聽講今晚好似嗌得落力左？"},{"pid":"03b1ef3ac6092ac849279572247c1c7f6888c5ca","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2737f2e63166d664c4f1b119af76faf7a6d4823","tid":1517920,"uid":127739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:40:08.000Z","msg":"聽講今晚好似嗌得落力左？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T14:54:38.000Z","msg":"今晚聽到有小朋友一齊嗌<br />\n表示感動<br />\n<br />\n聽晚繼續 大聲d <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沒有暴徒 只有暴政<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91f9bb997b961dce3c660707d6da3e8f7b350d7","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:53:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6ed2b7342a582f1b4e2a18e9d108eb66f32d263","tid":1517920,"uid":152630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T06:48:13.000Z","msg":"搭單問 柏傲灣有冇tg group?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f2630b586cf08f23349617b2d784bfaccc64bf","tid":1517920,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"點解會有 tg group <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點 add 到咁多人"},{"pid":"e6855b4614a3af951ed7e16027042bcde93b9283","tid":1517920,"uid":275280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71f2630b586cf08f23349617b2d784bfaccc64bf","tid":1517920,"uid":126100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T08:56:12.000Z","msg":"點解會有 tg group <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點 add 到咁多人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T11:35:53.000Z","msg":"因為原意係未收樓果陣<br />\n<br />\n大家一齊傾下d準備收樓資訊<br />\n<br />\n最後越add越多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}